        &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
       &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
          CNTraveler: 
         &lt;a href="https://www.cntraveler.com/story/how-to-eat-your-way-through-genoa-italys-most-underrated-city"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.cntraveler.com/story/how-to-eat-your-way-through-genoa-italys-most-underrated-city"&gt;https://www.cntraveler.com/story/how-to-eat-your-way-through-genoa-italys-most-underrated-city&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
